{"tid":1023174,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有一隻Game嘅職業系統係以現實為主題嘅話...會唔會係咁樣","createTime":"2019-02-15T14:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T15:20:25.000Z","uid":225916,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6d79af2414df48a32aabe5be7cb9097f0f2c5670","tid":1023174,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:31:31.000Z","msg":"近戰型職業：<br />\n地盤佬<br />\n<br />\n基本防具：安全鞋，安全帽，反光衣<br />\n<img src=\"https://19ga.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/20031730_1508041559262447_4178467023347931150_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F19ga.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F20031730_1508041559262447_4178467023347931150_n.jpg&h=96aeb932&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武器類：水喉通、平水尺(輕型中距離武器)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img7.hc360.cn/pic-7/busin-pic-261/7-261-33887261.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg7.hc360.cn%2Fpic-7%2Fbusin-pic-261%2F7-261-33887261.jpg&h=79b53e23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n錘仔(近距離重型武器)<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/84/Claw-hammer.jpg/220px-Claw-hammer.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F8%2F84%2FClaw-hammer.jpg%2F220px-Claw-hammer.jpg&h=476aaae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n磚頭(投擲暗器)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20160308/large/08la1p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20160308%2Flarge%2F08la1p2.jpg&h=b00a459e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n竹棚用竹(重型長距離武器)<br />\n<img src=\"https://m.chinawbk.com/images/hk/Webh_C_ykHFh_C_yF4SjUjebh_C_ybVH8_P_9MMKNKwFO1bMbUFOwMODg1NUxgpDO4g1Uh_C_yGWxJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.chinawbk.com%2Fimages%2Fhk%2FWebh_C_ykHFh_C_yF4SjUjebh_C_ybVH8_P_9MMKNKwFO1bMbUFOwMODg1NUxgpDO4g1Uh_C_yGWxJ.jpg&h=06eaa06e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機械類：電鑽、磨機(短距離高殺傷武器)，挖泥車，鑽土機<br />\n<br />\n部分職業可以加上：夜視鏡，防毒面罩....<br />\n<br />\n基本上物理攻擊嚟計<br />\n地盤佬一定係短距離戰鬥最強<br />\n力量同體力成長一定爆錶<br />\n操控同機動性可能較低<br />\n<br />\n仲可以轉2轉做唔同職業<br />\n例如搭棚工，扎鐵，釘板，燒焊<br />\n<br />\n輔助加補師：<br />\n醫生<br />\n<br />\n裝備:聽筒，手術刀，醫生袍<br />\n<br />\n基本上係醫師加上輔助型角色<br />\n技能:補血(要有一定機率斷錯症變扣血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，buff (攻擊力/血量加成)， debuff(麻痹，緩速)<br />\n攻擊主要係毒屬性攻擊：打毒針，落毒藥 仲有解剖，割內臟<br />\n<br />\n召喚師職業：<br />\n港女/女神<br />\n裝備：各大名牌子衣襪<br />\n攻擊武器：手袋<br />\n技能：召喚狗公，觀音兵，十四巴<br />\n加上可以幫男性角色戰力同補血?<br />\n被動技能：男性角色攻擊免疫（gay除外)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家一齊諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw後半我真係懶得搵圖<br />\n容許我懶少少 簡短啲<br />\n真係有人睇先繼續打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩職業想睇可以講低我盡量諗"},{"pid":"53d8e01e987a8376a9bb9ee712f77a374c8381a6","tid":1023174,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:33:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"168158d826f1b4982ebed839cfaf8309867a3f58","tid":1023174,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0559b87527c8b730354cff94bfdd2d7128da8fb8","tid":1023174,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:37:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736ce49ecbb8407455fab66263841f3d57754735","tid":1023174,"uid":42927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:40:22.000Z","msg":"醫生絕招：愛滋針<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b4f5b6e5a9afefaed1b11657775998e79de978","tid":1023174,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"736ce49ecbb8407455fab66263841f3d57754735","tid":1023174,"uid":42927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:40:22.000Z","msg":"醫生絕招：愛滋針<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:42:55.000Z","msg":"落毒包埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n算係debuff<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47732a1a276d8690d61f0be9996539d59af00af7","tid":1023174,"uid":86360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:42:58.000Z","msg":"地盤佬機動性不知幾撚高 <br />\n擒高擒低"},{"pid":"0754da5f9425d920b858a30166add82caaf627a9","tid":1023174,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:44:13.000Z","msg":"倫敦金會有咩技能優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae27e2cd29f005289007dd799cfa25391d134c9e","tid":1023174,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:44:16.000Z","msg":"雙失毒撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ca75c90b62cb276d3a057cd79839667f488aa3","tid":1023174,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47732a1a276d8690d61f0be9996539d59af00af7","tid":1023174,"uid":86360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:42:58.000Z","msg":"地盤佬機動性不知幾撚高 <br />\n擒高擒低"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:45:33.000Z","msg":"唔想寫到咁無敵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁好多都上左年紀行得冇咁快嘛<br />\n<br />\n機動性為主嘅我諗住寫落另一個職業"},{"pid":"daf6e6074c1978dcaab8abb928783ddbc0ea4b5f","tid":1023174,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0754da5f9425d920b858a30166add82caaf627a9","tid":1023174,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:44:13.000Z","msg":"倫敦金會有咩技能優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:54:15.000Z","msg":"好高難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n金融/倫敦金佬<br />\n裝備:老西，名錶<br />\n有保鏢旁身<br />\n可以打電話叫古惑仔斬人<br />\n技能:騙財(偷錢偷裝)，呃人、語言偽術(暈技)<br />\n可以無限屌閪 令其他人妒忌 造成心理傷害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6a279ed17ea199d664e23990eb7c8d6422d7f5","tid":1023174,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:57:02.000Z","msg":"倫敦金佬可以加落召喚師行列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男嘅就老千，女嘅就係臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2785d68151f2e295ef0b71ef36c7850ee036308e","tid":1023174,"uid":14737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae27e2cd29f005289007dd799cfa25391d134c9e","tid":1023174,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:44:16.000Z","msg":"雙失毒撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:03:38.000Z","msg":"毒屬性靈氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n裝備: baleno full gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n武器: 鍵盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f5175d3fa2ea228e35ab233fa150af29d76991","tid":1023174,"uid":27632,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:06:02.000Z","msg":"警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有槍（重型超遠程），警棍（輕型近戰程），手扣（控制技）<br />\n<br />\n二轉有<br />\n臥底，隱形技（限時兩年半），一擊必殺（只能用一次，唔係敵死就自己死）<br />\n<br />\n飛虎隊,，多種重型武器，近戰max<br />\n<br />\n警犬隊，召喚術（警犬），追蹤技（畀佢發現就走唔甩）<br />\n<br />\nPTU，防暴盾（能擋近戰及輕型遠程攻擊），催淚彈（範圍控制技）<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6681fce55389bbd01087c67f5d1c55f823f7a81","tid":1023174,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2785d68151f2e295ef0b71ef36c7850ee036308e","tid":1023174,"uid":14737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae27e2cd29f005289007dd799cfa25391d134c9e","tid":1023174,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T